Term-ANSIColor-Print version 0.03
=================================

This module is a simple way to create strings with ANSI color
markup. The interface is intended to be simple to read and use.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Readonly

